flowchart LR
  U[Human Conductor] --> HQueue[Hermes Queue tasks.json]
  HQueue --> HProfiles[Profiles: primary runner and sidecar profiles]
  HProfiles --> HTmux[tmux worker sessions]
  HTmux --> HWorktree[Worktree or Scratch Workspace]
  HWorktree --> HReceipt[final.md Receipt]
  HReceipt --> HWatcher[Watcher / Status Synthesis]

  U --> CSession[Codex Interactive Session]
  CSession --> CSub[Native Subagents]
  CSub --> CTools[Tools, Shell, MCP, Plugins]
  CTools --> COut[Consolidated Response]

  COut -. refactor target .-> CLane[Codex Lane Runner]
  CLane --> CQueue[Queue + Leases + Heartbeats]
  CQueue --> CReceipt[Schema Receipts + Provenance]
